paper_abstract: In this study, we analyze the experimental results in Gong et al. (2008), and find that the box plots of the coverage metric in solving the five three-objective problems are wrong. The corresponding corrected box plots are presented. The corrected results are still consistent with the original conclusions.
paper_title: Corrections on the Box Plots of the Coverage Metric in "Multiobjective Immune Algorithm with Nondominated Neighbor-based Selection"
